name: Hawaii Girl - Jumpy Game For Kids
name_original: Hawaii Girl - Jumpy Game For Kids
description:
Absolutely FREE and super fun adventure!

Discover new islands - jump from land to land!

Compete with your FRIENDS and beat the world record!

Pole vault from land to land
Avoid the patrol birds
Do not jump on the bombs
Catch the parrot and get an extra life!

Maybe you will be on the top of the leaderboard! Become the master of jumping - Hawaii Girl wants your help!

Hawaii Girl - Jumpy Game For Kids is waiting for you!
